---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../styles/legal.css';
---

<BaseLayout
  lang="en"
  title="Return Policy | Ilaaj AI"
  description="Ilaaj AI provides digital healthcare services. Learn how returns are handled for our digital consultations and prescriptions."
  canonical="https://www.ilaaj.ai/return-policy"
  keywords="ilaaj AI return policy, digital service return Pakistan, telemedicine return policy"
>
  <main>
    <section class="legal-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="legal-hero__icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary-600)" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="9 14 4 9 9 4"/><path d="M20 20v-7a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h1 class="legal-hero__title">Return Policy</h1>
        <p class="legal-hero__meta">Last updated: June 4, 2026</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="legal-body">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="legal-content">
          <div class="legal-section">
            <h2>Digital Services</h2>
            <p>Ilaaj AI provides digital healthcare services — AI-assisted consultations and doctor-verified prescriptions delivered electronically through our app. We do not sell or ship physical products, so traditional product returns do not apply.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="legal-section">
            <h2>Cancellations</h2>
            <p>You may cancel a consultation before it begins at no charge. Once a consultation has started or a prescription has been issued, the service is considered delivered and cannot be returned.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="legal-section">
            <h2>Service Issues &amp; Refunds</h2>
            <p>If a paid service was not delivered, was charged in error, or could not be completed due to a fault on our end, you may be entitled to a refund. Please review our <a href="/refund-policy">Refund Policy</a> for full eligibility and timelines.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="legal-section">
            <h2>How to Raise a Request</h2>
            <p>Email <strong>hello@ilaaj.ai</strong> with your registered phone number or email and the transaction details. We will respond within <strong>3 business days</strong>.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="legal-section legal-section--highlight legal-contact">
            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:hello@ilaaj.ai">hello@ilaaj.ai</a></p>
            <p><strong>Phone:</strong> +92-324-819-9663 (Mon–Fri, 9AM–6PM PKT)</p>
            <p><strong>Address:</strong> Office 7, Plot 782, Block G4, Phase 2, Johar Town, Lahore, 54782, Pakistan</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
